On pages that contain gadgets with outdated or invalid locations the entire contents of the page fails to load. Only the error message from the gadget is displayed.

For example, an outdated Greenhopper gadget present on a Confluence page will fail to locate the gadget and display only the following error message and none of the other content on the page.

